                                        1768
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Although incredibly promising for their low environmental impact and maintenance costs, PMFC technology is still under development. These biofuel cells have several dependability issues that limit their widespread use and industrialization. We can articulate the nature of their shortcomings into three main points as follows."
                                }
                            ]
